    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those seeking dependable transportation without the premium price of a showroom-ready car. While the engine and transmission are sound and have been regularly serviced, the exterior shows visible signs of use, including some noticeable scratches, minor dings, and fading on the trim. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear consistent with its age. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done and is ready for its next owner.",
