    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_24_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_24",
      "description": "Hey there! If you've been looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new, you have to see this beauty! It\u2019s in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one, and it still has that fresh, showroom feel. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m honestly sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to be obsessed with it! Come check it out and see for yourself!",
